<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Livestock Export Report</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --green-900: #1f6b2f;
            --green-800: #2a7a35;
            --green-700: #2f8a3a;
            --green-100: #eaf5ea;
            --green-50: #f7fbf7;
            --line: #2d8a3b;
            --text: #223126;
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            background: #ffffff;
            color: var(--text);
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        }

        .report {
            width: 100%;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding-bottom: 34px;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #236c2f 0%, var(--green-900) 100%);
            color: #fff;
            padding: 16px 22px 10px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .header-brand {
            font-size: 30px;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .header-sub {
            margin-top: 4px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
        }

        .header-center {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0;
        }

        .header-right {
            text-align: right;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
        }

        .content {
            padding: 14px 28px 0;
        }

        .intro-line {
            height: 4px;
            background: #d5ead7;
            margin: 0 0 12px;
        }

        .title {
            margin: 0;
            color: #1d5f2c;
            font-size: 29px;
            font-weight: 900;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--line);
            padding-bottom: 4px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .meta {
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.65;
            color: #39463c;
        }

        .meta strong {
            color: #203226;
        }

        .table-wrap {
            margin-top: 14px;
            border: 2px solid var(--line);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        thead th {
            background: var(--green-700);
            color: #fff;
            text-align: left;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        thead th + th {
            border-left: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
        }

        tbody td {
            padding: 9px 12px;
            font-size: 13px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e7eee6;
        }

        tbody tr:nth-child(even) {
            background: var(--green-50);
        }

        .footer {
            position: fixed;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #235f2c 0%, #1f5b29 100%);
            color: #fff;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            padding: 12px 18px;
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .footer .muted {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
            font-size: 11px;
        }

        .footer .center {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer .right {
            text-align: right;
        }

        .brand-lockup {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .brand-lockup img {
            width: 42px;
            height: 42px;
            object-fit: contain;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
            border-radius: 50%;
            padding: 4px;
        }

        @media print {
            @page {
                size: A4 portrait;
                margin: 0;
            }

            body {
                background: #fff;
            }

            .report {
                min-height: auto;
            }

            .footer {
                position: fixed;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="report">
        <header class="header">
            <div>
                <div class="header-brand">EL FIRMA</div>
                <div class="header-sub">Professional Livestock Management</div>
            </div>
            <div class="header-center"></div>
            <div class="header-right">Export: {{ generated_at }}</div>
        </header>

        <main class="content">
            <div class="intro-line"></div>
            <h1 class="title">Livestock Export Report</h1>

            <div class="meta">
                <div><strong>Export date:</strong> {{ generated_at }}</div>
                <div>As livestock manager at EL FIRMA, this report summarizes all registered livestock units.</div>
                <div>For each unit, livestock type and associated production are listed for monitoring and decision-making.</div>
                <div>This document serves as a practical farm management summary.</div>
            </div>

            <section class="table-wrap">
                <table>
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th style="width: 55%;">Livestock Type</th>
                            <th>Production</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        {% for item in elevages %}
                            <tr>
                                <td>{{ item.type_elevage ?: 'N/A' }}</td>
                                <td>{{ item.production ?: 'N/A' }}</td>
                            </tr>
                        {% else %}
                            <tr>
                                <td colspan="2">No livestock found.</td>
                            </tr>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </section>

            <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #7a8478; margin-top: 6px;">
                Total: {{ total_count }} livestock unit(s) registered
            </div>
        </main>

        <footer class="footer">
            <div>
                <div style="font-weight: 800;">EL FIRMA</div>
                <div class="muted">Professional Livestock Management</div>
            </div>
            <div class="center">Page 1 / 1</div>
            <div class="right">
                <div style="font-weight: 800;">Manager:</div>
                <div class="muted">{{ manager_name }}</div>
            </div>
        </footer>
    </div>

    <script>
        window.print();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
